As a new type of think tank with Chinese characteristics, Renmin Chongyang has hired dozens of former politicians, bankers, and renowned scholars from around the world as senior researchers, with the aim of paying attention to reality, providing advice to the country, and serving the people. At present, the National People's Congress Chongyang has 7 departments and 4 operation and management centers (Ecological Finance Research Center, Global Governance Research Center, China US Cultural Exchange Research Center, and China Russia Cultural Exchange Research Center). In recent years, the National People's Congress Chongyang has gained high recognition both domestically and internationally in research areas such as financial development, global governance, major country relations, and macroeconomic policies.

description_trans: On March 30, 1993, Henan Traffic Radio was established with FM 104.1. On November 1, 2013, the Henan Traffic Radio "Jiaoguang" helicopter successfully made its maiden flight in Zhengzhou, becoming the first dedicated helicopter in Henan for road navigation and media emergency response. name: 北方法制报
description: 《北方法制报》是吉林日报报业集团系列报刊之一，是全省惟一公开出版发行的法制类专业报。《北方法制报》创刊于1992年1月，前身系省公安厅主办的《北方公安报》；1999年，《北方公安报》更名为《北方法制报》。2003年 10月，《北方法制报》从省公安厅划归吉林日报报业集团管理。长期以来，《北方法制报》坚持宣传依法治国方略，维护国家法律尊严，普及群众法律知识，提升公众法律素养，立足政法，面向社会，宣传法制，弘扬正气，以案说法，警策人生，对推进法治吉林、平安吉林建设发挥了积极作用。
description_trans: Northern Legal Daily is one of the series of newspapers and magazines of Jilin Daily Newspaper Group, and is the only legal professional newspaper publicly published and distributed in the province. The Northern Legal Daily was founded in January 1992, formerly known as the Northern Public Security Daily sponsored by the Provincial Public Security Department; In 1999, the Northern Public Security Daily was renamed as the Northern Legal Daily. In October 2003, the Northern Legal Daily was transferred from the Provincial Public Security Department to the management of Jilin Daily Newspaper Group. For a long time, the Northern Legal Daily has adhered to promoting the strategy of governing the country by law, safeguarding the dignity of the country's laws, popularizing legal knowledge among the masses, enhancing public legal literacy, based on politics and law, facing society, promoting the rule of law, promoting righteousness, using cases to explain, and warning people's lives. It has played a positive role in promoting the construction of a rule of law and a safe Jilin.

name: 烟台音乐广播
description: 音乐在路上，风景在耳边。悦动调频FM105.9，一套类型化音乐广播。 每天早上7点到9点半播出的《晨光音乐行》，快节奏、有活力的音乐伴随热点话题互动、即时路况播报。傍晚时分的脱口秀节目《音乐副驾驶》，整合网络热点，用爆笑脱口秀演绎大事小情。午后休闲类音乐节目《摩卡时光》，突出时尚文艺气息、休闲放松的节奏和氛围。《光阴的故事》讲述音乐背后的故事、晚间《那些年，我们追过的歌》一起倾听经典怀旧歌曲。 全天14档的半点三分钟新闻《1059听天下》、每逢整点的《1059气象站》，滚动播出的《小雪私房歌》、《1059国学馆》、《股市连连听》、《1059车生活》等3分钟线性小专栏，让听众在欣赏音乐的间隙，快节奏享用新闻资讯、天气信息、股市动态、趣味国学、爱车宝典等丰富的各项服务。
description_trans: Music on the road, scenery in my ears. Yuedong FM 105.9 is a set of categorized music broadcasting. The "Morning Music Tour" is broadcasted every morning from 7:00 to 9:30, with fast-paced and energetic music accompanied by interactive hot topics and real-time traffic updates. The evening talk show "Music Co pilot" integrates internet hotspots and uses hilarious talk shows to portray big and small events. The afternoon leisure music program "Mocha Time" highlights the fashionable and artistic atmosphere, as well as the relaxed rhythm and atmosphere. "The Story of Time" tells the story behind music, and in the evening, "The Songs We Chased in Those Years" listens to classic nostalgic songs together. The half hour and three minute news "1059 Listening to the World" and the hourly "1059 Meteorological Station", as well as the rolling 3-minute linear columns such as "Little Snow Private Song", "1059 Chinese Academy", "Stock Market Listening", and "1059 Car Life", allow listeners to enjoy a variety of services such as news, weather information, stock market trends, fun Chinese culture, and car enthusiasts while enjoying music.

description_trans: China Railway Shenyang Group Co., Ltd., formerly known as Shenyang Railway Bureau, was established in 1956 and is a subsidiary of China National Railway Group Co., Ltd. It focuses on railway passenger and freight transportation services and implements diversified operations. The economic attraction zone covers the entire territory of Liaoning and Jilin provinces, as well as 32 prefecture level cities (prefectures) in parts of Inner Mongolia Autonomous Region, Heilongjiang and Hebei provinces. As of the end of September 2020, the operating mileage of the group's managed railways was 14377.4 kilometers, including 11299.6 kilometers of conventional railways and 3077.8 kilometers of high-speed railways. In terms of passenger transportation, a total of 366.5 pairs of passenger train crew tasks were undertaken, and 212 pairs of high-speed trains were operated. In terms of freight transportation, the main transportation characteristics are coal transportation from the west to the east, grain transportation from the north to the south, and port transportation. It plays an important role in providing logistics services that connect the coast and hinterland, and achieve "customs clearance to the sea". It is one of the largest railway group companies in the country, with more than 193000 employees.

description_trans: Quantuo Technology (Hangzhou) Co., Ltd. has been focusing on big data application solutions in the fields of digital economy, smart city, and big data marketing for a long time, providing data intelligence services such as strategic analysis and decision-making, smart population profiling, data security, data governance, and scenario marketing for enterprises and governments. The enterprise has now formed a complete data ecosystem industry chain, including big data+live streaming, big data+catering, big data+cultural and creative, big data+medical, big data+education, etc. It has R&D departments such as data security, data mining, data profiling, data application models, data algorithms, and has cooperated with many well-known universities to establish big data R&D laboratories for joint research and project development. In recent years, Quantuo Technology has continued to make efforts in the direction of smart cities. Currently, it is collaborating with local governments in Shanghai, Hangzhou, Ningbo, Cangzhou, Huanghua, and other cities to build big data industry ecological parks and intelligent manufacturing industry parks. With rich experience in smart city construction, Quantuo Technology is driving the development of local technology enterprises, promoting digital industrialization and full factor digitization as the main line, and promoting the deep integration of digital technology and the real economy. In addition, Quantuo Technology strengthens the key role of data resources in the construction of smart cities by utilizing new generation information technologies such as 5G, artificial intelligence, cloud computing, and blockchain. It empowers public services, modern governance, ecological livability, and industrial economy with data, coordinates green development and smart city construction, promotes the sustainable development of green and low-carbon smart cities under the digital economy, and focuses on promoting the construction of digital government, green industry, and smart society.

name: 隆安发布
description: 隆安县位于广西西南部，隶属南宁市管辖，隆安寓“兴隆发达，长治久安”之意，因县城形似蝴蝶，又称“蝶城”。隆安县城距离南宁市中心80公里、距机场70公里，属南宁市“一小时经济圈”，南宁至昆明铁路、云桂高速铁路（在建）、南宁至百色高速公路和二级公路，以及右江航道穿境而过。境内物产丰富，凤凰山银矿储藏量全国第二，粮食作物以水稻、玉米为主，经济作物有甘蔗、香蕉、板栗、木薯等，是“中国板栗之乡”。旅游资源有龙虎山、绿水江漂流、仙缘谷、布泉风光、榜山文塔、惠迪公祠、雁江老街等风景名胜。境内发现的大龙潭石铲遗址属新石器时代晚期文化遗址，是世界上发现的最大的大石铲祭祀群，其出土的楔形双肩大石铲成为广西博物馆的“镇馆之宝”，2013年6月隆安县被中国民协授予“中国‘那’文化之乡”称号。受理违法和不良信息举报方式：后台留言或评论；电话：0771-6529983；邮箱：larmt@qq.com。也可进入南宁市互联网举报·辟谣平台”网站进行举报，链接：http://www.nnjbpy.org.cn
verified_reason: 广西隆安县委宣传部官方微博
description_trans: Long'an County is located in the southwest of Guangxi and is under the jurisdiction of Nanning City. Long'an symbolizes "prosperity and prosperity, long-term stability", and is also known as "Butterfly City" due to its butterfly like shape. Long'an County is 80km away from the center of Nanning and 70km away from the airport, belonging to Nanning's "one hour economic circle". Nanning Kunming Railway, Yunnan Guangxi High speed Railway (under construction), Nanning Baise Expressway and second-class highway, as well as Youjiang Waterway pass through. The territory is rich in natural resources, with Fenghuangshan silver ore reserves ranking second in the country. The main grain crops are rice and corn, and the economic crops include sugarcane, bananas, chestnuts, cassava, etc. It is known as the "hometown of Chinese chestnuts". Tourism resources include scenic spots such as Longhu Mountain, Lushui River Drifting, Xianyuan Valley, Buquan Scenery, Bangshan Wenta, Huidi Temple, and Yanjiang Old Street. The Dalongtan Stone Shovel Site discovered within the territory belongs to the late Neolithic cultural site, which is the largest group of large stone shovel worship found in the world. The wedge-shaped double shoulder large stone shovel unearthed from it has become the "treasure of the Guangxi Museum". In June 2013, Long'an County was awarded the title of "China's' Na 'Cultural Hometown" by the China Association for the Betterment and Progress of the People. The way to accept reports of illegal and harmful information: leave messages or comments in the background; Telephone: 0771-6529983; Email: larmt@qq.com . You can also go to the website of Nanning Internet Report and Rumour Rejection Platform to report. The link is: http://www.nnjbpy.org.cn
verified_reason_trans: Official Weibo account of the Propaganda Department of Long'an County Party Committee in Guangxi

description: 河南理工大学大学生通讯社（简称大通社）成立于1985年，是在校党委宣传部的直接领导下，由校团委、校报编辑部指导开展活动的新闻性综合类学生社团，为我校成立最早的学生社团之一。在日常工作中，通讯社以《河南理工大学报》为主阵地，以校园网为依托，承担着我校内外宣传的部分任务。其主要工作围绕校园新闻展开，涉及校报新闻、校园网新闻的采写，通讯的策划与采写，文学稿的征集、采写与排版等，致力打造成为集新闻、文学、编辑、活动、交流于一身的河南理工大学第一宣传组织。

description_trans: Established in 1985, Henan University of Technology College Student News Agency (abbreviated as Datong Society) is a news oriented comprehensive student club under the direct leadership of the school's Party Committee Propaganda Department, guided by the school's Youth League Committee and the school newspaper editorial department to carry out activities. It is one of the earliest student clubs established in our school. In daily work, the news agency takes the "Henan University of Technology Newspaper" as the main platform and relies on the campus network to undertake some of the tasks of internal and external publicity of our school. Its main work revolves around campus news, involving the collection and writing of school newspaper news and campus network news, communication planning and collection, literary manuscript collection, collection and layout, etc. It is committed to becoming the first propaganda organization of Henan University of Technology that integrates news, literature, editing, activities, and communication.
